A. No. Because once the decision was made a couple weeks ago to go with MSNBC and 
I haven't -- I have just been aware of basically what has happened, the dispute with Mr. 
Murdoch and the lawsuits and so forth. They just come very quickly.  
 
Since they didn't pay any attention to me before, I don't know why they would now.  
 
Q. What is your recommendation now? 
 
MR. JOFFE: Wait a second. 
 
THE WITNESS: I don't have a recommendation.  
 
