A. That's right. City Hall meetings. High school or courses in college courses.  
 
What do you call it where you learn how to be a plumber or something like that? Things 
that- are of benefit to the local community, usually community oriented programming.  
 
Q. Does that mean they shouldn't show any international news at all?  
 
A. I don't know. I haven't got an opinion on that. But there is lots of other sources for 
national and international news on the commercial channels.  
 
